Phoenix Mecano Logo
Phoenix Mecano AG is a Swiss technology company based in Stein am Rhein. The company manufactures enclosures and components for industrial uses and is divided into three divisions – DewertOkin Technology Group, Industrial Components and Enclosure Systems. Phoenix Mecano is present at more than 60 locations worldwide and has major production sites and development centres in Germany, Hungary, Tunisia, India and China. In 2020, the company employed around 7,500 people worldwide and generated sales of 686.
